d\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes from Brazil, Canada, and several African countries are also expected to be in Metz, according to POC secretary general Atty.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9997765227131366, \"rank\": 0.00021456799292423958, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9434785563747433, \"rank\": 0.05982477889770243, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metz\", \"score\": 0.9949404358593373, \"rank\": 0.005085286322956424, \"text\": \"Metz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metz\"}, {\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.554145086314576e-31, \"text\": \"POC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wharton Chan.\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1754, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wharton_School_of_the_University_of_Pennsylvania\", \"score\": 0.998818340785393, \"rank\": 0.0011830433214503125, \"text\": \"Wharton\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wharton_School_of_the_University_of_Pennsylvania\", \"dbpedia\":