3052, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3076, \"end\": 3092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Nepomuceno\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Nepomuceno\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Nepomuceno\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Nepomuceno\"}, {\"begin\": 3178, \"end\": 3183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994897735, \"rank\": 5.103882527135334e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He ran both the 100m and 200m dash, but was not able to advance to the final round of both events.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3301, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nepomuceno, also a United States Navy sailor, died at just 39 years old in 1939.\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3322, \"end\": 3340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"score\": 0.9999999997994564, \"rank\": 1.8859997685680842e-10, \"text\": \"United States Navy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Navy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After falling short multiple times, the Philippines first achieved a gold-medal finish when Diaz ruled the 55-kilogram weightlifting category in the postponed Tokyo Games, held in 2021 in the middle of the coronavirus pandemic.\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3425, \"end\": 3436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.418270922764228e-19, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sadly, Diaz will not get a shot at an Olympic golden double as shefailed to qualifyfor Paris.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3709, \"end\": 3720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler.com\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": []}]}"